duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide high quality patient care to patients suffering from ESRD
Build relationships and bonds with patients and their families
Utilize dialysis experience to optimize patient care
Create care plans and treatment strategies for individual patients
Demonstrate empathy and sensitivity in patient interactions
Think critically and make informed decisions in patient care
Communicate effectively with patients, families, and healthcare team
Maintain a current state nursing license

education_certification.credential: Graduated from an accredited school of nursing
